1. git init, create README.md
2. create LICENSE
3. npm init, complete package.json
4. add .gitignore
5. create gitpod.yml and gitpod.Dockerfile, config terminals and .env creation with gitpod url for port 3000
6. install react react-dom as deps; webpack webpack-cli webpack-dev-server webpack-merge as dev-deps
7. install babel-loader @babel/core @babel/preset-env @babel/preset-react html-webpack-plugin as dev-deps
8. create src/js src/assets; create index.js and favicon.ico
9. create html template and complete basic webpack files configuration, require dotend and use gp url port 3000 as public prop for devServer webpack module
10. webpack configuration based on config folder with paths.js, wbpk-dev-server.js, wbpk-dev-config.js and wbpk-prod-config.js
11. create Home view and add scripts to package.json; dev server should be running with react on localhost:3000
12. install style-loader css-loader sass-loader node-sass as dev-deps
13. install bootstrap react-bootstrap
14. configure rules for css/scss files
15. create src/sass and styles.scss and _main.scss; import bootstrap scss and _main on styles.scss
16. create Layout.js and complete Home, import styles from index.js
17. create loader styles and render Layout based on boolean loader control state changed after children mountin simulation (setTimeout 2secs)
18. server should be running with bootstrap and custom styles, loading for 2 seconds before rendering home view
19. install file-loader eslint eslint-loader eslint-plugin-react prettier prettier-webpack-plugin as dev-dep and prop-types as dep
20. create .eslintrc config file and add eslint-loader in webpack, as well as prettier webpack plugin with rules
21. install eslint-plugin-react-hooks as dev-dep and add configuration on eslintrc.json file
22. install react-router-dom and add BrowserRouter to Layout as well as new view About.js
23. create folders and files for AppContext and flux.js; complete components and imoprt in Layout
24. create folders and files for a loaderReducer to make Layouts loader work as useReducer example
25. install @babel/runtime and @babel/plugin-transform-runtime; add in webpack config
26. install @babel/plugin-proposal-class-properties; add in webpack config
27. add contest view as example for state and context features